  "str_1519": "💡 Health Tip",
  "str_1520": "💾 Save Today's Symptoms",
  "str_1521": "📦 Order Free Reusable Pads",
  "str_1522": "Locate the nearest youth center distributing free reusable pads, or order them to be delivered quietly.",
  "str_1523": "Find Distributor",
  "str_1524": "🧼 Hygiene &amp; Washing Guide",
  "str_1525": "<strong>Soak in cold water:</strong> Always soak your reusable pad in cold water first. Hot water sets blood stains.",
  "str_1526": "<strong>Wash with soap:</strong> Use regular body soap or washing soap. Gently rub the fabric together until clean.",
  "str_1527": "<strong>Dry in direct sunlight:</strong> This is critical. Direct sunlight kills bacteria. Do not dry in damp, hidden areas.",
  "str_1528": "<strong>Store safely:</strong> Keep in a clean, dry bag ready for next month.",
  "str_1529": "Pad Order",
  "str_1530": "Select your district to find the nearest free distribution zone or place an anonymous order.",
